{sqlitecore} Features

1. frictionless(?) storage of #RStats objects in SQLite DB
2. Calling R funcs from within SQLite

SQLite example:
* store data.frames in DB
* SQLite calls R func  & stores ggplot result in DB col
* Later, can fetch ggplot directly from the DB https://t.co/AOthxzg7IE

Not all the ideas for {sqlitecore} are really "rock solid" -> a lot of code churn.

e.g. many re-writes of how to handle SQLite's very lax type affinity - which is why I'm playing with #ListFrames to try & come up with a more sound approach

Release: Next month maybe?
